AB  - This document elaborates guidance on advancing good locally led practices through GCF modalities. Part 1 introduces GCF’s parameters and approach to devolution in the GCF business model and elaborates approaches for context-specific models. Part 2 provides step-by-step guidance for developing and structuring funding proposals in alignment with the parameters. A set of annexes cover Readiness, local, traditional and Indigenous knowledge, a related checklist and relevant examples from GCF portfolio.
